title: Bach, JS - Flute Sonatas - Hewitt, Oliva
description:
Bach, JS: Three Flute Sonatas.

In 2013, Hyperion released a glorious disc of Bach's flute sonatas by Angela Hewitt (piano) and Andrea Oliva (flute). They included three sonatas written by Bach and three sonatas attributed to Bach. Now, I hope you don't think me unduly pedantic, but I have only included here the three sonatas actually written by Bach. (My reasoning is as follows: When I sit down to listen to Bach, my desire is to listen to music written by-how should I put this?-Bach!)

Please enjoy.

MP3 @ 320
